Introduction

Han Seung Yun, also known simply as Yun, is a South Korean singer. He is a member the band D82 and was a member of the duo LUNAFLY, and the boy group NZN. He released his first solo single, ‘Wonder Land,’ in 2017. His official solo debut came with the mini album ‘Lovender’ on February 15th, 2022.
